          "description": "Dr. Michael Dann, is an exceptional gastroenterologist. He cares about his patients. He takes the time to listen attentively, and never makes you feel rushed or dismissed. What really stands out is his amazing memory\u2014he remembers details about your history and concerns without you having to repeat yourself.\n\nHe is absolutely top-notch and sets the standard for what a doctor should be: attentive, compassionate, and deeply knowledgeable. I always feel heard, supported, and confident in his care. Highly recommend.",
